{"type": "article", "id": 27505, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-05-30T07:04:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 28279, "name": "Bellaphone"}, {"id": 28280, "name": "Tea house"}, {"id": 28281, "name": "SmartBike"}, {"id": 28282, "name": "duo"}, {"id": 28283, "name": "Mollo"}, {"id": 28284, "name": "Bedow"}, {"id": 28285, "name": "Fiddle ＋ Hammer"}, {"id": 24474, "name": "Vanmoof"}, {"id": 28286, "name": "Mimi Jung"}, {"id": 28287, "name": "Fumie Shibata"}, {"id": 28105, "name": "Philippe Malouin"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702145758KWytzunMlbAeD0JZ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<p>          </p>\n<h2>Bellaphone by Fiddle ＋ Hammer</h2>\n<p>美国密尔沃基的家具公司 Fiddle + Hammer 一直都致力于用最好的素材制作出视觉与听觉上都能带给人享受的产品，最近他们就推出了这款巨大的音箱 <a href=\"http://fiddlehammer.com/#/bellaphoneno7/\">Bellaphone</a> 。它的特别之处在于采用回收来的龙舌兰和威士忌酒桶制成，使得音乐更加“醉人”。木材质的喇叭造型不仅起到了放大音乐的效果，看上去也很像是一个来自留声机时代的传家宝。起初，这个音箱是由公司的创办人，雕塑家兼小提琴家 Jordan Waraksa 设计来专门播放自己创作的音乐的，现在已经投入量产。如果需要订购的话可以通过<a href=\"http://fiddlehammer.com/\">官网</a>联系他们。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021559408Um64OF3dazWVfEQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.90953545\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155941MNSo9ErmUciFK30W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.81662592\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155941jxyD21RouWehmVg9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.80929095\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021559425Y0kPAao27M3SdVf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75794621\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021559437VEyOvWGAdmfHi6Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74938875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155945vfd5Tmea461Wyswr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49877751\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Tea house by Mimi Jung</h2>\n<p>如果你喜欢一个人静静地喝茶，Mimi Jung 设计的这个<a href=\"http://www.mimijung.com/tea-house\">独立茶室</a>是一个不错的选择。除了宗教与文化元素，Jung 富有现代感的诠释进一步强调了安慰以及自省的力量。茶室的圆柱形框架可以通过旋转的方式进行开关，通过半透明的墙壁使人与外部环境隔离。茶室内还配备了一张低矮的木桌，供人饮茶小坐或是进行冥想。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155946lGBy4djmTOF0Qh6H.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.686\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021559478Js7fw5NRgSWM3E4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.686\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155948AczGM1Hqjb6Dtp2P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.638\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155949ATfvBpWPS3yUskIO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.721\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155950xJHVsrqTNCMhUj76.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.651\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155950dloa5Y7CqOM0VgcL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.658\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>SmartBike by VanMoof</h2>\n<p>老丢自行车的朋友们，这辆由阿姆斯特丹自行车公司 VanMoof 推出的 SmartBike 或许是你的福音。这款自行车的上管前端配备了 GSM 和蓝牙追踪系统，被盗后 VanMoof 的团队会为车主定位自行车的位置。VanMoof 还提供了一个在购买后的前两年完全免费的服务：如果在失窃后的两周内没有办法物归原主，VanMoof 会为车主替换一辆新的自行车。SmartBike 还是一辆无锁的自行车，车主可以通过配套的手机应用或者是把手放在上管上解锁自行车。如果你对这个智能的自行车感兴趣的话，可以通过<a href=\"https://www.vanmoof.com/en_us/bikes/smart-straight\">链接</a>订购，售价为 1098 美元起。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155951pwc0jizG4PFUvtgq.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155952Vt6gLvIHi4kP7JBn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155952DRZd8Cn3yFMImxHU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6992665\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155953RrFAVXPZDp6Jk5mU.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155953vCpniczHAwWs79hl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6992665\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155954M5SfAlmoabeKJrPG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62469438\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>duo by Fumie Shibata</h2>\n<p>在家休息时，打开香薰机已经成为不少人的选择。免去清洗和加水的烦恼，日本设计师 Fumie Shibata 为品牌 @aroma 设计了一款可以随时切换香味的压电式香薰机 <a href=\"http://www.at-aroma.com/duo/\">duo</a>，香味的扩散范围最大可以达到 70 平方米。通过上端的按钮可以对 duo 进行定时或者是切换香味，在设定的时间内机器就会自动运行。这是它的<a href=\"http://store.at-aroma.com/products/detail.php?product_id=589\">购买链接</a>，售价为 54000 日元。配套的 @aroma 香油则需要额外购买。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021559548NfjaKeBLbvCdqh0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62727273\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155955LfWBqDp3I7UHzn4T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62727273\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155955CyLjYRKTMQr135ZA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62727273\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155956JLjUeiBxR5lQdEAs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62727273\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Mollo by Philippe Malouin</h2>\n<p>我们之前曾经介绍过加拿大设计师 Philippe Malouin 设计的一款<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/27290.html\">日食壁灯</a>，这次他延续了自己一贯的简约风格，为 <a href=\"http://establishedandsons.com/\">Established and Sons</a> 设计了名为 <a href=\"http://philippemalouin.com/new-gallery-1/\">Mollo</a> 的扶手椅。圆鼓鼓的 Mollo 外型非常简单，内部柔软的泡沫材料会让人深陷其中，很适合坐下小憩。目前，这款手扶椅仅能在 Established and Sons 的专卖店购买。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155956SdW4IsOnmPvUcAQg.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155957czetAOHsS2vkwn5j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.78515625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155958bq62QjIA9pCyVJw8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021559581lXuxSBC9HQnpTtZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Böcklingpastej by Bedow</h2>\n<p>请不要误会，它并不是鱼味的牙膏，而是 <a href=\"http://bedow.se/\">Bedow</a> 为瑞典一间家族企业 Biggans 的鱼酱设计的包装。棕色纸板外盒印着海浪的图案，内部装有蓝绿底色的管状鱼酱，而当你翻到盒底的时候，还能惊喜地发现海星和水草，就好像潜到了海底一样。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155959Bc1kniMKY37wJTbr.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702155959KCnokXZMJcQxLP1z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160000aYFpgEyH6L2bn3Uk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160000pXqfJg6BRVwuOeMW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702160001E8ykunjqGi4QRtlv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}